Fourteen Fires012759aer223s38mkyw2p46x56qkj52eyj40d1785882015-03-22T18:37:11ZThe Dragon Demands5014364[[Image:Ancient Valyrian Shepherds Fourteen Fires.png|thumb|300px|The ancient Valyrians first found the dragons in the Fourteen Fires.]]
The '''Fourteen Fires''' was a chain of volcanoes located in the [[Valyria]]n peninsula, in the continent of [[Essos]]. It was in this location where Valyrians, then a community of shepherds, first discovered [[dragons]].

The Fourteen Fires exploded four hundred years ago in a massive volcanic eruption, a cataclysmic event known as the [[Doom of Valyria]], which destroyed the Valyrian civilization and shattered the Valyrian peninsula. The entire region was consumed by the oceans, creating the [[Smoking Sea]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Valyria and the Dragons]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
